									Need an MVP or automation system you can put to work?
								</h2>

								<p class='text-lg text-zinc-300 dark:text-zinc-600 leading-relaxed max-w-xl'>
									Book a 30-minute roadmap call. We&rsquo;ll narrow the problem and figure out whether I&rsquo;m the right fit for it.
								</p>

								<div class='pt-2'>
									<a
										class='btn-primary inline-block border-[#090909] bg-[#090909] px-6 py-3 text-white hover:bg-white hover:text-black focus-visible:ring-2 focus-visible:ring-primary focus-visible:ring-offset-2 dark:border-[#090909] dark:bg-[#090909] dark:text-white dark:hover:bg-white dark:hover:text-black'
										href={BOOK_CALL_URL}
										target='_blank'
										rel='noopener noreferrer'
										data-track-event='book_call_clicked'
										data-track-location='footer_contact'
